        <item>
            <title>1.0.53</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 09:11:25 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>53</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.53</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[- Saves the text you're actively typing in a note before quitting, archiving, deleting, or running an in-app update — so your latest words are never left behind.
- The Support item in the menubar dropdown now opens Settings directly on the Support tab.
- Improved note storage path handling for broader macOS version compatibility, and made pre-update backup failures non-blocking so a backup hiccup can't stop your notes from being saved.
]]></description>
